description:
THE EDITED SUBJECT - NR.02
The Edited Subject is about capturing the ordinary, then changing its original entity, to an abstracted artwork, that still has reminiscent of what it was, and allows the viewer to fill the in the puzzle pieces of the added abstractness.


---

RESOLUTION : 3508x4961 (A3 SIZE / 300 DPI)
You are allowed to print this artwork for NON-COMMERCIAL/PERSONAL USE. For best results, I strongly suggests printing it as RHISO or SCREEN PRINT, since it's designed with those mediums in mind.
